==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rocking-stone
<hw>Rock"ing-stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A stone, often
of great size and weight, resting upon another stone, and so exactly
poised that it can be rocked, or slightly moved, with but little
force.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rockless</ent>⟦br⟧
